(41, 1, 'Alice in Borderland, Vol. 1', 'Haro Aso', '9781974728374', 2022, 'Comics & Graphic Novels', 'An action-packed thriller and source of the hit Netflix drama where the only way to survive is to play the game! Battle Royale: Angel\'s Border; Deadman Wonderland; Death Note; Zom 100 The first game starts with a bang, but Ryohei manages to beat the clock and save his friends. It‚Äôs a short-lived victory, however, as they discover that winning only earns them a few days‚Äô grace period. If they want to get home, they‚Äôre going to have to start playing a lot harder.', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=IgyMzgEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=IgyMzgEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&source=gbs_api', 'Fair', '2025-12-29 22:55:41', '2026-01-12 19:47:25', 344, 0, NULL),
